name: Car Availability
query:
select 
distinct v.name as 'Car:Data:100',
case COALESCE(si.name,IFNULL(si.name,''))
WHEN '' THEN 'Available'
ELSE 'BOOKED' END AS 'Status:Data:100',
si.name as "BookingReference:Link/Sales Invoice:180",
si.delivery_from_time_cf as "Delivery_From_Time" ,
si.delivery_to_time_cf as "Delivery_To_Time",
si.return_from_time_cf as "Return_From_Time",
si.return_to_time_cf as "Return_To_Time"
from `tabVehicle` AS v
LEFT JOIN `tabSales Invoice` as si 
ON v.name = si.vehicle_cf
AND si.posting_date = %(as_on_date)s
